Name: Secret Laboratory
About the game: Secret Laboratory In a Secret laboratory, experiments were conducted on people. Something went terribly wrong... The subjects escaped the lab and started killing everyone. It is your mission to terminate the experiment while fighting hordes of monsters. Secret Laboratory is a shooter with multiple options. You can play first person or third person, in a very fast and easy way to change. Around the lab there are many weapons, including pistols, rifles and even a sword and shield. You must quickly find your gear and survive endless waves of enemies. FEATURES : - Beautiful, realistic graphics. - Many types of weapons. - Multiple gameplay: first person or third person. - Time-Bullet
